No [G]turning [A]back, no tur-[D]ning back
{end_of_bridge}

{start_of_bridge: label="Bridge 1 JP"}
[Bm]主のあと[G]を一ついてゆ[A]ーく [Bm]
[G]全てを [Bm]捨てて[A]も
